FOLDER.NAME: EDWTD_SALES_ORDERS
FOLDER.DESCRIPTION: This is for EDW TeraData Sales Orders and POS Track PM:Vinit verma

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT SCA.POS_SCAAC_KEY , SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT , POS_TRX.BASE_LIST_UNIT_PRDT_PRICE_AMT , POS_TRX.DSTRBTR_RPTD_CST_UNT_PRC_AMT , POS_TRX.VALIDATED_NET_UNT_PRC_USD_AMT AS VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, POS_TRX.VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMT AS VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT , PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG , PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT , SK3_SC_ID_INT AS SC_ID_INT, SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG AS SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM , SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM, SALES_CREDIT_START_DTM AS START_TV_DTM, EXPIRATION_DTM AS END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG, POS_TRX.POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AS SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ COALESCE( POS_LN.DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD,'UNKNOWN') AS DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, COALESCE( POS_LN.POS_RETURN_ROLE,'=') AS POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$NRTNCRVWDB.N_POS_SCA_ADJ_CNG_DRCT_NRT_TV SCA INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LN_DELTA_TV POS_TRX ON SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LINE POS_LN /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ ON POS_LN.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT WHERE SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM >'$$LastExtractDate' AND SCA.START_TV_DTM >'$$LastExtractDate' AND COALESCE(SALES_CREDIT_DUPLICATE_FLG ,'N') = 'N' AND PD_BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CD = 'L' AND SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT BETWEEN POS_TRX.START_TV_DT AND POS_TRX.END_TV_DT
UNION
SELECT SCA.POS_SCAAC_KEY , SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT , POS_TRX.BASE_LIST_UNIT_PRDT_PRICE_AMT , POS_TRX.DSTRBTR_RPTD_CST_UNT_PRC_AMT , POS_TRX.VALIDATED_NET_UNT_PRC_USD_AMT AS VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, POS_TRX.VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMT AS VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT , PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG , PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT , SK3_SC_ID_INT AS SC_ID_INT, SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG AS SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM , SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM, SALES_CREDIT_START_DTM AS START_TV_DTM, EXPIRATION_DTM AS END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG , POS_TRX.POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AS SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ COALESCE( POS_LN.DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD,'UNKNOWN') AS DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, COALESCE( POS_LN.POS_RETURN_ROLE,'=') AS POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$NRTNCRVWDB.N_POS_SCA_ADJ_CNG_DRCT_NRT_TV SCA INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LN_DELTA_TV POS_TRX ON SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LINE POS_LN /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ ON POS_LN.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT WHERE SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM >'$$LastExtractDate' AND SCA.START_TV_DTM >'$$LastExtractDate' AND SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG = 'Y' AND PD_BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CD = 'L' AND SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT BETWEEN POS_TRX.START_TV_DT AND POS_TRX.END_TV_DT
UNION
SELECT SCA.POS_SCAAC_KEY , SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT , POS_TRX.BASE_LIST_UNIT_PRDT_PRICE_AMT , POS_TRX.DSTRBTR_RPTD_CST_UNT_PRC_AMT , POS_TRX.VALIDATED_NET_UNT_PRC_USD_AMT AS VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, POS_TRX.VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMT AS VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT , PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG , PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT , SK3_SC_ID_INT AS SC_ID_INT, SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG AS SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM , SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM, SALES_CREDIT_START_DTM AS START_TV_DTM, EXPIRATION_DTM AS END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG, POS_TRX.POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY, SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AS SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ COALESCE( POS_LN.DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD,'UNKNOWN') AS DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, COALESCE( POS_LN.POS_RETURN_ROLE,'=') AS POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$NRTNCRVWDB.N_POS_SCA_ADJ_CNG_DRCT_NRT_TV SCA INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LN_DELTA_TV POS_TRX ON SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LINE POS_LN /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ ON POS_LN.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT WHERE SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM > ( SEL LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.CTL_ETL_LAST_EXTRACT_DATES WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID = 'wf_WI_POS_SCA_INCR_SC' ) AND SCA.START_TV_DTM <= '$$LastExtractDate' AND SCA.END_TV_DTM = '3500-01-01 00:00:00' AND PD_BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CD = 'L' AND (COALESCE(SALES_CREDIT_DUPLICATE_FLG ,'N') = 'N' OR SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG = 'Y') /* ADDED AS A PART OF HANDLING SOURCE COMMIT ISSUE */ AND SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT BETWEEN POS_TRX.START_TV_DT AND POS_TRX.END_TV_DT AND NOT EXISTS ( SEL 1 FROM $$SLSORDVWDB.N_DRVD_SCA_POS_ADJ_DETAILS N_DRVD WHERE N_DRVD.SK_TRX_SALES_CREDIT_ID_INT = SCA.SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AND DV_LATEST_FLG = 'Y' AND N_DRVD.SK_TRX_SALES_CREDIT_ID_INT <> - 999)
UNION
SELECT SCA.POS_SCAAC_KEY , SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT , POS_TRX.BASE_LIST_UNIT_PRDT_PRICE_AMT , POS_TRX.DSTRBTR_RPTD_CST_UNT_PRC_AMT , POS_TRX.VALIDATED_NET_UNT_PRC_USD_AMT AS VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, POS_TRX.VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMT AS VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT , PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG , PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT , SK3_SC_ID_INT AS SC_ID_INT, SCA.SOURCE_DELETED_FLG AS SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM , SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM, SALES_CREDIT_START_DTM AS START_TV_DTM, EXPIRATION_DTM AS END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG , POS_TRX.POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AS SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ COALESCE( POS_LN.DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD,'UNKNOWN') AS DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, COALESCE( POS_LN.POS_RETURN_ROLE,'=') AS POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,POS_LN.RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$NRTNCRVWDB.N_POS_SCA_ADJ_CNG_DRCT_NRT_TV SCA INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LN_DELTA_TV POS_TRX ON SCA.PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_POS_TRANSACTION_LINE POS_LN /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ ON POS_LN.BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT= POS_TRX.BK_POS_TRX_ID_INT WHERE SCA.EDW_UPDATE_DTM > ( SEL LAST_EXTRACT_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.CTL_ETL_LAST_EXTRACT_DATES WHERE JOB_STREAM_ID = 'wf_WI_POS_SCA_INCR_SC' ) AND SCA.LAST_UPDATED_DTM <= '$$LastExtractDate' AND SCA.START_TV_DTM BETWEEN ( CAST('$$LastExtractDate' AS TIMESTAMP(0)) - INTERVAL '15' MINUTE) AND '$$LastExtractDate' AND COALESCE(SALES_CREDIT_DUPLICATE_FLG ,'N') = 'N' AND PD_BK_SALES_CREDIT_TYPE_CD = 'L' AND SCA.DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT BETWEEN POS_TRX.START_TV_DT AND POS_TRX.END_TV_DT AND NOT EXISTS ( SEL 1 FROM $$SLSORDVWDB.N_DRVD_SCA_POS_ADJ_DETAILS N_DRVD WHERE N_DRVD.SK_TRX_SALES_CREDIT_ID_INT = SCA.SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT AND N_DRVD.SK_TRX_SALES_CREDIT_ID_INT <> -999 )

SELECT POS_SCAAC_KEY, PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT, BASE_LIST_UNIT_PROD_PRICE_AMT, DISTI_RPTD_COST_UNIT_PRICE_AMT, VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT, PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY , COALESCE(SC_TEAM.SHR_IND_SALESREP_NUMBER , INCR.PD_SALES_REP_NUM ) AS PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG, /*COALESCE(SC_TEAM.SHR_IND_SPLIT_PERCENT * 100, INCR.PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT ) AS PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT,*/ CASE WHEN SC_TEAM.SHR_IND_SPLIT_PERCENT IS NULL THEN INCR.PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT ELSE (SC_TEAM.SHR_IND_SPLIT_PERCENT * INCR.PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT) END PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT,/* modified as part of team split CR by ugandhav */ SC_ID_INT , SOURCE_DELETED_FLG , LAST_UPDATED_DTM , DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT , START_TV_DTM , END_TV_DTM , DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG , POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , NET_CHANGE_PROCESS_DT , SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT , /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,INCR.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,INCR.RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,INCR.RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$STGDB.WI_POS_SCA_INC_NET_CHG_DT INCR LEFT JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_OTM_PHX_SC_TEAM SC_TEAM ON SC_TEAM.SC_ID=INCR.SC_ID_INT WHERE INCR.START_TV_DTM <> INCR.END_TV_DTM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT POS_SCAAC_KEY, PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT, BASE_LIST_UNIT_PROD_PRICE_AMT, DISTI_RPTD_COST_UNIT_PRICE_AMT, VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT, PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG, PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT, SC_ID_INT, SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, LAST_UPDATED_DTM, DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, START_TV_DTM, END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG, POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , CASE WHEN CAST(START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) = FISCAL_MONTH_END_DATE AND Cast(Substr(Cast( START_TV_DTM As varchar(20)),12,19) As Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) BETWEEN CAST ('00:00:00' AS Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) AND CAST('23:59:59' AS Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) THEN CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) WHEN CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) = FISCAL_MONTH_START_DATE AND Cast(Substr(Cast( START_TV_DTM As varchar(20)),12,19) As Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) BETWEEN CAST ('00:00:00' AS Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) AND CAST('19:29:59' AS Interval Hour(2) To Second(0)) THEN CAST ( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) WHEN ( CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE) > FISCAL_MONTH_START_DATE AND CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE) < FISCAL_MONTH_END_DATE ) AND ( START_TV_DTM BETWEEN CAST (CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) - INTERVAL '1' DAY AS TIMESTAMP(0) ) + INTERVAL '19:30' HOUR TO MINUTE AND (CAST(CAST(START_TV_DTM AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP(0) ) + INTERVAL '19:30' HOUR TO MINUTE ) ) THEN CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) WHEN ( CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE) >= FISCAL_MONTH_START_DATE AND CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE) < FISCAL_MONTH_END_DATE ) AND ( START_TV_DTM BETWEEN CAST(CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE) AS TIMESTAMP(0) ) + INTERVAL '19:30' HOUR TO MINUTE AND CAST (CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) + INTERVAL '1' DAY AS TIMESTAMP(0) ) + INTERVAL '19:30' HOUR TO MINUTE ) THEN CAST( START_TV_DTM AS DATE ) + INTERVAL '1' DAY END AS NET_CHANGE_PROCESS_DATE , PDC.PROCESS_DATE, SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT FROM ( SELECT POS_SCAAC_KEY, PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT, BASE_LIST_UNIT_PROD_PRICE_AMT, DISTI_RPTD_COST_UNIT_PRICE_AMT, VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT, PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG, PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT, SC_ID_INT, SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, LAST_UPDATED_DTM, DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, START_TV_DTM, END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG, POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY , SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$STGDB.WI_POS_SCA_INCR_POS WI_POS
UNION
SELECT POS_SCAAC_KEY, PD_BK_POS_TRANSACTION_ID_INT, BASE_LIST_UNIT_PROD_PRICE_AMT, DISTI_RPTD_COST_UNIT_PRICE_AMT, VLDTD_NET_UNIT_PRICE_USD_AMT, VALUATION_PRICE_USD_AMOUNT, PD_SALES_TERRITORY_KEY, PD_SALES_REP_NUM, DISTRIBUTOR_OFFSET_FLG, PD_SALES_COMMISSION_PCT, SC_ID_INT, SOURCE_DELETED_FLG, LAST_UPDATED_DTM, DV_LAST_UPDATED_DT, START_TV_DTM, END_TV_DTM, DISTRIBUTOR_BUCKET_FLG, POS_TRX_LN_PRDT_QTY, SK_TRX_SC_ID_INT, /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ DSV_OR_POS_TYPE_CD, POS_RETURN_ROLE /*ADDED AS PART OF DSV Q1FY16*/ /* ADDED AS PART OF JUNE 2018 RELEASE AMY-NRT SCOPE*/ ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_START_DTM ,RU_SERVICE_CONTRACT_END_DTM ,RU_SRVC_CNTRCT_DRTN_MNTHS_CNT
FROM $$STGDB.WI_POS_SCA_INCR_SC WI_SCA WHERE NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM $$STGDB.WI_POS_SCA_INCR_POS WI WHERE WI_SCA.POS_SCAAC_KEY = WI.POS_SCAAC_KEY ) ) WI , $$COMREFVWDB.R_FISCAL_DAY_TO_YEAR FDY, (SELECT PROCESS_DATE FROM $$ETLVWDB.BKG_PROCESS_DT_CNTRL ) PDC WHERE CAST(WI.START_TV_DTM AS DATE) = FDY.CALENDAR_DATE
